{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "66bcbe35ae81d148616b1775", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 3, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 180, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "MOG", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76e4c52ffa3c944600e1"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eba6"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "64b850022a7d64ecd80b00a8", "title": "NEET 2008 (Screening)", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "If $M(A, Z), M_P$ and $M_n$ denote the masses of the nucleus ${ }_Z^A X$, proton and neutron respectively in units of $u\\left(1 \\mathrm{u}=931.5 \\mathrm{MeV} / c^2\\right)$ and $\\mathrm{BE}$ represents its binding energy in $\\mathrm{MeV}$, then", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "tQCYZ", "text": "$M(A, Z)=Z M_p+(A-Z) M_n-\\mathrm{BE} / c^2$", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "vKS2p", "text": "$M(A, Z)=Z M_p+(A-Z) M_n+\\mathrm{BE}$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "LPrbR", "text": "$M(A, Z)=Z M_p+(A-Z) M_n-B E$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "lHXkA", "text": "$M(A, Z)=Z M_p^P+(A-Z) M_n^n+B E / c^2$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "Binding energy of a nucleus containing $N$ neutrons and $Z$ protons is\n$\\begin{aligned}\n& \\mathrm{BE}=\\left[N M_n+Z M_p-M(A, Z)\\right] c^2 \\\\\n\\Rightarrow & \\frac{\\mathrm{BE}}{c^2}=N M_n+Z M_p-M(A, Z) \\\\\n\\Rightarrow & \\frac{\\mathrm{BE}}{c^2}=(A-Z) M_n+Z M_p-M(A, Z) \\\\\n\\Rightarrow & M(A, Z)=Z M_p+(A-Z) M_n-\\mathrm{BE} / c^2\n\\end{aligned}$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGNEPYQ62722285", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "bucket": "", "isRemoved": false, "updatedAt": "2024-08-29T17:47:42.098Z", "up